worksforme: <p>
There is a short-term fix I'e applied for now to solve my issue. Not the prettiest one but it works.
</p>
<pre class="wiki">add_filter( 'wp_insert_post_data', 'rm_wp_insert_post_data', '99', 2 );
function rm_wp_insert_post_data ( $data , $postarr ) {
  return str_replace("\xc2\xa0", " ", $data);
}
</pre>
